00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:57.030
and they basically spin
your blood in a centrifuge,

00:14:57.030 --> 00:14:58.650
and then after they
do microneedling,

00:14:58.650 --> 00:15:02.150
they put that all
over your face.

00:15:02.150 --> 00:15:05.820
It looks crazy, but
it really does work.

