00:50:06.660 --> 00:50:08.160
to your staff, to--

00:50:08.160 --> 00:50:09.990
you've got major,
major challenges

00:50:09.990 --> 00:50:14.250
to deliver, both deliver
services and deliver confidence

00:50:14.250 --> 00:50:15.785
and beauty, as people are.

00:50:15.785 --> 00:50:17.160
So what are you
doing about that?

00:50:17.160 --> 00:50:18.355
MICHELLE LEE: Well, I want
mental health services.

